>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>co\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>n\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>s\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ulis\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cnum value=\"3\">III\u003C/num>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>abn\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>epti\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"line\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text of Prado from autopsy, after Eck and Barbera\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                    \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>For Pompeia Sosia Falconilla, daughter of the consul Q. Pompeius Sosius Priscus, granddaughter of the consul Q. Pompeius Falco, great-granddaughter of the consul Q. Sosius Senecio, great-great-granddaughter of the consul Sextus Iulius Frontinus...\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n                \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#FP\">\n                    \u003Cp>Per Pompeia Sosia Falconilla, figlia di Q. Pompeius Sosius Priscus console, nipote di Q. Pompeius Falco, console, pronipote di Q. Sosius Senecio console, pronipote di Sextus Iulius Frontinus console…\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#FP\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Orsi\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1900\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>49 no.17\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UE3VRJA7\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001707\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001707\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
